scrot - capture a screenshot

Read the man page to learn how to use this utility.

Dependencies:

Fedora:

  $ sudo dnf install meson imlib2-devel libX11-devel

Debian, Ubuntu:

  $ sudo apt install meson libimlib2-dev libx11-dev

Build instructions:

  $ meson setup build
  $ ninja -C build
  $ ninja -C build install

This utility works in X11-based environments only - it does not work inside
Wayland or XWayland sessions.
